MODULE SXConstruct
CATEGORY Realization
DESCRIPTION constructs a regular field with regular connections
INPUT object; field;  (no default); object to define extent of new field
INPUT lower; vector;  (no default); explicit lower bounds of new field
INPUT upper; vector;  (no default); explicit upper bounds of new field
INPUT deltas; scalar or vector;  (no default); increment for each axis
INPUT counts; integer or vector;  (no default); number of positions along each axis
OUTPUT output; field; output field
